    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO THE SET...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/e9646c5df0f247b5fbafe430bdc8f3a4.poster.avif?t=1763528391\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/e9646c5df0f247b5fbafe430bdc8f3a4.webm?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/e9646c5df0f247b5fbafe430bdc8f3a4.mp4?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the previous showrunner of beloved children’s TV series Mint’s Hints, you never expected to find yourself on set again - especially after the show had been abruptly cancelled. However, you find yourself corrected after being mysteriously abducted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT HINTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/67b33aded6d1b2c617ab9c242528be2f.poster.avif?t=1763528391\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/67b33aded6d1b2c617ab9c242528be2f.webm?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/67b33aded6d1b2c617ab9c242528be2f.mp4?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> It’s showtime like you’ve never experienced before. Find paw-shaped Hints with special ghost-detecting Flashbrights, and discover the secret behind the show’s closure with your Happy-Go-Lucky Notebook. Journey through the abandoned studio and its dark corridors, but be careful, the stars of the show are after you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE, AND RUN...!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/33f662e755cb583d2c9f2d30648ff676.poster.avif?t=1763528391\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/33f662e755cb583d2c9f2d30648ff676.webm?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150720/extras/33f662e755cb583d2c9f2d30648ff676.mp4?t=1763528391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Get a glimpse behind the scenes and uncover the secrets hidden beneath the Mint’s Hints original set in this thrilling puzzle adventure horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Average playtime: 30 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made in Unreal Engine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique yet intuitive gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original characters and lore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
